Title: Commending the Order of the Eastern Star Sunshine Chapter No. 34 upon the occasion of hosting its Five Point Tea Fundraiser on April 28, 2024
ActClause: LEGISLATIVE RESOLUTION commending the Order of the Eastern Star Sunshine Chapter No. 34 upon the occasion of hosting its Five Point Tea Fundraiser on April 28, 2024, and paying tribute to this year's honoree, Worthy Matron Thelma Herbert
